Element


citetitle
&citetitle.purpose;


&citetitle.synopsis.gen;
Description



CiteTitle provides inline markup for the
title of a cited work.


Processing expectations

&format.inline; Often italicized for Books and quoted
for Articles.



&FutureChanges;



&fu.interfacedefinition;




&citetitle.parents.gen;
&citetitle.children.gen;

Attributes

pubwork



Pubwork identifies the genre of the cited
publication.





See Also
